: \"apps\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Travel technology firm Sabre recently unveiled a new AI-powered retailing platform for airlines called SabreMosaic, which is meant to help airlines create and sell personalized retail experiences.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Travel technology firm Sabre\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"a new AI-powered retailing platform\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"airlines\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"SabreMosaic\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"airlines\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"personalized retail experiences\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Alaska Airlines is planning to launch a trip planner built with tech from Google.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1028, \"end\": 1043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska_Airlines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alaska Airlines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska_Airlines\"}, {\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9984065731658113, \"rank\": 0.0015959581227251967, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a trip planner\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"tech\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"IHG Hotels & Resorts has plans to release a trip planning tool powered by Google's AI within its One Rewards mobile app later this year.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.